{
  "id": "adv_event_2201_01_03",
  "title": "サニピの\nお正月",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_train-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "五人揃って電車に乗るのも久しぶりだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s been a while since the five of us took a train together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 3.8994558810999997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "最近は個人の仕事が増えて\nバラバラで行動することが多いものね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Recently we’ve had more solo jobs‚\nso we go in separate directions a lot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.1127892335,
      "endTime": 9.5037416299,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "train",
      "startTime": 9.7104083538
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "こんな時間でも電車は動いてるんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The trains are running even now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.7104083538,
      "endTime": 13.104898119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "train",
      "startTime": 13.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "お正月は初詣や初日の出を見に行く人が多いから\n夜中でも臨時列車が走ってるのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because a lot of people go out on New Year’s Day for the first sunrise or first shrine visit of the year.\nExtra trains are running even in the middle of the night.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.1666666667,
      "endTime": 21.2380498729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "train",
      "startTime": 21.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "おかげで間に合いそう……\nお正月の臨時列車、便利……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to them‚ it looks like we’ll be in time…\nExtra trains for New Year. That’s convenient.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.4333333333,
      "endTime": 26.6243086339,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "train",
      "startTime": 26.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "東京には夕方までに戻ればいいから\nこの分なら星見市でゆっくり過ごせそうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We don’t have to get back to Tokyo until evening.\nThat should allow us to take our time in Hoshimi City.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.8333333333,
      "endTime": 33.889455843200004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "train",
      "startTime": 34.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "みんなと一緒に初日の出を見るの、楽しみだな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m looking forward to seeing the first sunrise with you all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.1,
      "endTime": 37.9428345203,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 39.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "高台にとうちゃーく！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Here we are at the hill!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.2333333333,
      "endTime": 42.5021769126,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 42.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "さすがに一月の風は冷たいわね\nもっと厚着してきた方が良かったかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As expected‚ the January wind is icy.\nMaybe we should have dressed up warmer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.7,
      "endTime": 49.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "ですね。でも、太陽が出れば少しは暖かくなりそう……\n日の出までお喋りでもしながら待ちましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right‚ but it’ll probably get a bit warmer once the sun comes up.\nWe can chat while we wait for sunrise.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.5333333333,
      "endTime": 60.5493427968,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 60.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、初日の出を見た後は……どうしよう？\nすぐに東京に帰るの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚ what do we do after we see the sunrise?\nGo straight back to Tokyo?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.7333333333,
      "endTime": 68.10826634989999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 68.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "せっかく五人揃ってるんだから\n他にもお正月らしいことをしようよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ve got all five of us together for a change‚\nso there must be something New Year-ish to do!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.3,
      "endTime": 73.02436833189999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "お正月らしいこと……\n羽根つき、かるた、書き初め、初詣……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s “New Year-ish”?\nBattledore‚ karuta‚ first calligraphy of the year‚ first shrine visit…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.2333333333,
      "endTime": 82.1176190581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 82.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、この近くに神社があったわね\nあそこなら初詣出来るんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that you mention it‚ there’s a shrine near here.\nWe could do our first shrine visit there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.3333333333,
      "endTime": 88.3769158704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 88.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ初日の出を見た後は、みんなで初詣をしよう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ we’ll all make our first shrine visit after we see the first sunrise.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.5666666667,
      "endTime": 93.0460089366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 93.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "いいわね。そうしましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Cool‚ let’s do that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.2666666667,
      "endTime": 95.6686847846,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-evening",
      "startTime": 96.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "あ……空が明るくなってきたよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The sky’s getting brighter.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.9333333333,
      "endTime": 102.17861674619999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "太陽が昇ってきた……\n初日の出……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The sun’s rising.\nFirst sunrise…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.4,
      "endTime": 106.43357142779999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-evening",
      "startTime": 106.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ……綺麗……\n一面が光に染まっていく……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ that’s pretty…\nThe whole sky is filled with light.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.6,
      "endTime": 114.46666666670001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-evening",
      "startTime": 114.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "……サニーピース……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Sunny Peace…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.7666666667,
      "endTime": 117.2000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-evening",
      "startTime": 117.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "え？　何か言った？　怜ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? What did you say‚ Rei-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.4,
      "endTime": 120.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-evening",
      "startTime": 120.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "前にサニピの特集記事で書かれていたことを\n思い出したの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I remembered something that was written once in\na feature article about Sunny Peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.7,
      "endTime": 125.29129249469999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "太陽のような眩しさで観客を自然と笑顔にする\n光溢れるアイドルグループ。それがサニーピースだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“A light-filled idol group with a dazzling brightness like the sun\nwhich naturally makes the crowd smile. That’s Sunny Peace.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.8333333333,
      "endTime": 134.98151456410002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-evening",
      "startTime": 135.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "見る人を自然と笑顔にする眩しい光……\nなんとなく初日の出に似てるわね",
